{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [
    {}
  ],
  "wsWinStyles": [
    {}
  ],
  "wpWinPositions": [
    {}
  ],
  "events": [
    {
      "tStartMs": 120,
      "dDurationMs": 3640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "♫ I know you love me too, baby."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 4480,
      "dDurationMs": 1880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Don't wait just dive in tonight. ♫"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 6360,
      "dDurationMs": 1680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nHello, I'm Hannah Gelbart."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 8480,
      "dDurationMs": 3760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Welcome to this episode of What in\nthe World from the BBC World Service."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 12280,
      "dDurationMs": 2440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Today I'm speaking to Big Ocean,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 14720,
      "dDurationMs": 3560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "the world's first ever K-Pop boy band\nwith hearing loss."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 18280,
      "dDurationMs": 4560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They use lights, vibrations, and even\nsign language in their dance routines."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 22840,
      "dDurationMs": 4160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So in this episode, you're going to hear\nhow K-Pop is breaking down barriers"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 27000,
      "dDurationMs": 2640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and what it's like being a pop star\nwith hearing loss."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 30400,
      "dDurationMs": 3320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "♫ Baby, I just wanna get attention. ♫"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 33720,
      "dDurationMs": 3280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Hello and welcome to the podcast.\nIt's so great to have you here."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 37000,
      "dDurationMs": 3480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Can you introduce yourselves?\nYes. Attention!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 40480,
      "dDurationMs": 3120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "We are Big Ocean! Hi!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 43600,
      "dDurationMs": 880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nHi!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 44840,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I'm PJ, the main vocalist."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 47720,
      "dDurationMs": 4320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I'm Jiseok, the main dancer.\nI'm Chanyeon, the main rapper."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 52040,
      "dDurationMs": 3080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What are some of the challenges, PJ,\nthat you have faced"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 55120,
      "dDurationMs": 1640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nas a musician with hearing loss?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 56760,
      "dDurationMs": 3680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "One of the biggest challenges was\ndancing in sync."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 61200,
      "dDurationMs": 3440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So we have to come up with solutions."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 64640,
      "dDurationMs": 6240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So our company provided\nthe assistive devices like"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 71920,
      "dDurationMs": 5400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "vibrating smartwatches\nand placing lights on the screen."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 77320,
      "dDurationMs": 3840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "It was very helpful to us\nand through that system"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 81160,
      "dDurationMs": 6800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "we could match and\nsync well."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 87960,
      "dDurationMs": 4240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And there are other ways too."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 92240,
      "dDurationMs": 5920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "We use AI solutions and technology for"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 98360,
      "dDurationMs": 4920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "the overall upgrade for high quality music, yes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 103840,
      "dDurationMs": 1200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Chanyeon, what about you?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 105040,
      "dDurationMs": 2400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What are some of the challenges\nthat you have come across?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 135440,
      "dDurationMs": 4080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "When you were forming the band,\nwhat was it like then?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 139520,
      "dDurationMs": 3840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What were the challenges that\nyou faced during the training phases?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 143360,
      "dDurationMs": 2040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I understand that there used\nto be more members"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 145400,
      "dDurationMs": 1440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and some members dropped out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 181440,
      "dDurationMs": 4720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "PJ mentioned some of the things that\nyou used to overcome these challenges."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 186160,
      "dDurationMs": 4760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Things like having a watch with\na metronome and AI assistive technology."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 190920,
      "dDurationMs": 3400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Are there any other devices that you\nhave or anything that you do to try"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 194320,
      "dDurationMs": 3280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and help you make music together?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 197600,
      "dDurationMs": 5000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Oh, actually,\nwe have been training"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 202680,
      "dDurationMs": 5240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "with a top vocal teacher and a vocal lab also."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 207920,
      "dDurationMs": 3400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So when we practice the songs"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 211320,
      "dDurationMs": 6200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "we use the\nsmartphones and we can,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 217520,
      "dDurationMs": 2760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "we could see the high pitch."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 220280,
      "dDurationMs": 4960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So for example, when shouting the pitch,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 225280,
      "dDurationMs": 3040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nthen we can see it, visually."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 228320,
      "dDurationMs": 720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nLike a waveform?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 229040,
      "dDurationMs": 3160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Yeah, visually we could see that."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 232200,
      "dDurationMs": 2400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So it was very helpful to us. Yeah."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 267120,
      "dDurationMs": 1880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "That is really positive."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 269000,
      "dDurationMs": 4280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And one of the things that you do is\nmake your music accessible for people"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 273280,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "in the audience with hearing loss."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 275760,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Can you tell me a bit\nabout what you do in your live shows"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 278440,
      "dDurationMs": 2560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and in your music videos\nto make your music"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 281000,
      "dDurationMs": 2600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "as inclusive\nand accessible as possible?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 283600,
      "dDurationMs": 4360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "We combine singing,\ndancing and sign language"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 287960,
      "dDurationMs": 3800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "to create an inclusive experience\nfor everyone,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 291800,
      "dDurationMs": 7920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "for communication we use KSL, ASL and IS,\nInternational Sign Language."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 299920,
      "dDurationMs": 2640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "♫ I tried to make me believe."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 302680,
      "dDurationMs": 2760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "You were the story I wanted to read."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 305560,
      "dDurationMs": 3040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nBut my heart is sinking ♫"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 309000,
      "dDurationMs": 2000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "You know this, with the language"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 311000,
      "dDurationMs": 6280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "we can actually, when we meet\nour fans or in a fan meeting place"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 317280,
      "dDurationMs": 2600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "they show us"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 319880,
      "dDurationMs": 2400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "sign language for communication."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 322280,
      "dDurationMs": 4240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So when we see their communication"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 326520,
      "dDurationMs": 4000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I'm so grateful and so happy."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 330760,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And I wanted to find out about\nthe other things that are out there"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 333440,
      "dDurationMs": 2960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "to help people\nwith hearing loss experience music."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 336520,
      "dDurationMs": 4840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Here is Gavin Songer from the UK charity\nthe National Deaf Children Society."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 341360,
      "dDurationMs": 5680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Hi! People with hearing loss can\nexperience music in a variety of ways."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 347040,
      "dDurationMs": 3840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "For example, organisations such\nas Performance Interpreting"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 350880,
      "dDurationMs": 3760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "provide sign language interpreters\nat concerts and festivals"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 354640,
      "dDurationMs": 5640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "so those who cannot hear can access the\nmusic visually through sign language."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 360280,
      "dDurationMs": 2040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Those with\nthe more severe hearing loss"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 362320,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "often enjoy playing music\nwith a heavy bass."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 365520,
      "dDurationMs": 4640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "As these frequencies\ncan be felt physically on the body."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 370160,
      "dDurationMs": 5360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "There have also been instances of aromas\nand scents being introduced in venues"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 375520,
      "dDurationMs": 5120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "to give people a multisensory\nexperience at concerts through smell."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 380640,
      "dDurationMs": 4840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "There are various products available\nto help people with hearing loss access music."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 385560,
      "dDurationMs": 2800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Modern hearing aids\nand hearing implants"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 388520,
      "dDurationMs": 2120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "have integrated Bluetooth\nfunctionality."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 391120,
      "dDurationMs": 1600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So music from phones,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 392720,
      "dDurationMs": 4120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "or tablets can be streamed directly\nto the user's hearing device"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 396840,
      "dDurationMs": 2600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "without the need for headphones\nor speakers."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 402800,
      "dDurationMs": 4200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Those with conductive hearing loss\ncan use bone conduction headphones,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 407000,
      "dDurationMs": 3840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "which send sound waves through\nthe skull using vibrations instead of"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 410840,
      "dDurationMs": 2840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "through the ear. Also,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 413680,
      "dDurationMs": 4920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "while haptic vests and bodysuits have\nbeen primarily designed for gaming,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 418600,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "they can also be used by people\nwith hearing loss"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 421280,
      "dDurationMs": 3560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "to experience music\nthrough vibrations."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 424840,
      "dDurationMs": 4560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "There are apps available that can detect\nsongs playing in public places."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 429400,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "These apps can display\nreal time lyrics"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 432080,
      "dDurationMs": 3920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "so the listener can follow the words\nto the song."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 436000,
      "dDurationMs": 4280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Finally, last year,\nApple launched Music Haptics,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 440280,
      "dDurationMs": 4640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "which allows users to experience\nmusic on their iPhone with taps,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 444920,
      "dDurationMs": 2600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and they find vibrations\nthat are synchronised"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 447520,
      "dDurationMs": 1560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "with the music playing\nfrom their phone."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 452200,
      "dDurationMs": 3400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "How has the deaf community responded\nto your music?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 478280,
      "dDurationMs": 2120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And we have a video\nfrom one of your fans."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 480400,
      "dDurationMs": 4080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "This is Jade. She's a Big Ocean fan,\nand she has progressive hearing loss."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 484520,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Hey BBC, my name is Jade."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 487400,
      "dDurationMs": 5920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Big Ocean debuting was a giant win\nfor the deaf community"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 493320,
      "dDurationMs": 5960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "in the sense\nof just showing that we can."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 499280,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And then they continued making music\nand continued performing,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 502160,
      "dDurationMs": 4280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "improving their skills\nand their talents as performers"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 506440,
      "dDurationMs": 4360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and the way they interact with fans,\nit feels genuine."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 510800,
      "dDurationMs": 4800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They take sign language and they take\ntheir interpretations of the music,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 515600,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and they turn it into dance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 518280,
      "dDurationMs": 4440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And the way they do it makes it blend\nseamlessly into the choreography."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 522720,
      "dDurationMs": 1720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Like, you don't even notice\nit's there."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 524440,
      "dDurationMs": 5040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So I was diagnosed with\nprogressive hearing loss in 2023,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 529480,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "but I had been doing music since\nas long as I can remember."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 532680,
      "dDurationMs": 5880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I've been singing and playing\ndifferent instruments my whole life."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 538560,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "But I thought I was going\nto have to give it all up."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 541760,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And then a few months\nafter I was diagnosed,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 544240,
      "dDurationMs": 1600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Big Ocean was announced."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 545840,
      "dDurationMs": 5160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And I guess they gave me hope."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 551000,
      "dDurationMs": 4760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They gave me the confidence to continue\ndoing music and continue dancing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 555760,
      "dDurationMs": 6840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They have opened a door\nfor deaf performers"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 562600,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and just performers\nwith disability in general."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 565480,
      "dDurationMs": 6360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Not only that, Big Ocean helped me\ncome to terms with my own hearing loss."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 571840,
      "dDurationMs": 4360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They helped me accept it,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 576200,
      "dDurationMs": 5360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and they helped me feel confident\nin wearing my hearing aids"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 581560,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and made me feel like I wasn't alone."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 584440,
      "dDurationMs": 3680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "That must be very inspiring\nfor you all to hear."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 588120,
      "dDurationMs": 3760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Chanyeon, what is it like being\na disabled person in Korea?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 591880,
      "dDurationMs": 2560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "How does Korea treat people\nwith disabilities?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 627280,
      "dDurationMs": 4440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Jiseok, K-Pop is known\nfor being extremely competitive"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 631800,
      "dDurationMs": 2760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "through the training\nand the performances."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 634560,
      "dDurationMs": 3280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Do you think that the way\nit treats its idols is changing?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 697840,
      "dDurationMs": 3280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Before we go, I want to ask you\nif you can teach me some signs."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 701120,
      "dDurationMs": 4440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "When you come on the stage and you say\n\"We are Big Ocean\" and you sign it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 705560,
      "dDurationMs": 2960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What's the most common sign?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 708520,
      "dDurationMs": 3000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Oh...\"I love you.\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 711520,
      "dDurationMs": 2200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "\"I love you\" in Korean Sign Language.\nYeah."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 713720,
      "dDurationMs": 3560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Thank you.\n\"I love you\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 717280,
      "dDurationMs": 2080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "\"I love you\" in ASL.\nYes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 719360,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "American Sign Language.\nYeah."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 721840,
      "dDurationMs": 4160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "An in International Sign Language is \"I love you.\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 726000,
      "dDurationMs": 1400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "\"I love you.\"\n\"I love you.\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 727400,
      "dDurationMs": 2040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And can you do \"What in the World?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 734560,
      "dDurationMs": 1800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "World, what, right?\nWorld. What? Right."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 736360,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What in the World!\nNews."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 739560,
      "dDurationMs": 840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "News. Okay."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 740400,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "News in the world.\nSo it's kind of like news in the world."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 742880,
      "dDurationMs": 3880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So it's.\nOh, yes. That's right."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 746760,
      "dDurationMs": 960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "That's perfect."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 747720,
      "dDurationMs": 1360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Thank you so much,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 749080,
      "dDurationMs": 3280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "thank you so much for coming into\nthe studio, for telling me your stories,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 752360,
      "dDurationMs": 2320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "thank you so much\nfor being part of the podcast."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 754680,
      "dDurationMs": 1720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Oh, thank you so much."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 756400,
      "dDurationMs": 2000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nAnd thank you for joining us."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 758400,
      "dDurationMs": 3560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I'm Hannah Gelbart. This is What in\nthe World from the BBC World Service"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 761960,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and we'll be back with\nanother episode soon. See you then. Bye."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 764840,
      "dDurationMs": 2200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Bye!\nThank you for having us."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
